WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 29=

01:46.990 --> 01:47.860
How nice to be young.

01:48.470 --> 01:50.060
Duan Xu is so fearless

01:50.060 --> 01:51.910
and stubborn that he won't turn back.

01:52.470 --> 01:53.990
He's quite like me in my younger days.

01:58.300 --> 01:59.300
Actually,

02:00.750 --> 02:02.190
you didn't have to do all this.

02:02.500 --> 02:03.340
Ziji,

02:06.700 --> 02:07.540
these past ten years,

02:07.860 --> 02:09.110
as one so high above,

02:12.460 --> 02:13.700
you stay by a mortal like me.

02:14.790 --> 02:16.070
It must've been hard on you.

02:17.790 --> 02:19.390
In the past, I was young, defiant,

02:19.390 --> 02:20.300
and angry at the world,

02:20.900 --> 02:22.230
but now I have let it all go.

02:23.620 --> 02:25.510
You should return where you belong.

02:26.670 --> 02:27.670
All that you have done

02:29.300 --> 02:30.350
is meaningless.

02:31.830 --> 02:32.670
As you know,

02:33.420 --> 02:34.260
I won't live long.

02:36.830 --> 02:38.180
I know what I'm doing.

02:39.510 --> 02:40.350
Drink the medicine.

02:41.700 --> 02:42.860
If you truly want to save me,

02:43.070 --> 02:44.420
get me some elixir instead.

02:46.110 --> 02:48.550
Mortals should take mortal medicine.

03:06.350 --> 03:07.390
By order of His Majesty,

03:07.950 --> 03:09.252
the Minister of War is suspected

03:09.263 --> 03:10.140
of horse graft

03:10.620 --> 03:11.673
and has now been detained.

03:11.933 --> 03:13.289
The remaining evidence against him

03:13.300 --> 03:14.740
is here in the 5th Prince's Mansion.

03:15.056 --> 03:16.300
Any documents tied to this case

03:16.300 --> 03:18.043
are to be taken back
to the Judicial Review

03:18.070 --> 03:18.950
for investigation.

03:19.990 --> 03:20.830
- Yes.
- Yes.

03:28.020 --> 03:28.860
Your Highness,

03:29.740 --> 03:30.580
for the time being,

03:31.140 --> 03:32.550
please stay in the mansion

03:33.180 --> 03:35.270
until His Majesty finds the truth.

03:51.399 --> 03:52.752
Something's happened to my father.

03:53.140 --> 03:53.980
Duke Pei

03:54.270 --> 03:55.580
has stopped caring for us two.

04:03.460 --> 04:04.990
That is a mortal matter.

04:06.020 --> 04:07.140
It has nothing to do with me.

04:08.900 --> 04:10.270
We still have one last chance.

04:10.733 --> 04:11.892
I can take you to the palace.

04:11.950 --> 04:12.896
I can make you Emperor.

04:12.990 --> 04:14.990
You can have anything you want.

04:14.990 --> 04:15.830
No.

04:16.740 --> 04:18.240
Do not make me enter the palace again.

04:20.470 --> 04:22.260
He Simu left a magical artifact there.

04:22.670 --> 04:23.590
Song Xingyu,

04:24.350 --> 04:25.190
I am right here.

04:36.710 --> 04:38.500
What a fine thing.

04:38.710 --> 04:39.699
It sealed away at least

04:39.710 --> 04:40.846
the lifelong spirit power

04:40.857 --> 04:41.913
of three mighty sorcerers.

04:42.180 --> 04:43.230
No wonder it could block

04:43.230 --> 04:44.790
Great Ancestor's spiritual aura search.

04:56.790 --> 04:57.990
We have a pact.

04:58.289 --> 04:59.629
If you want to live, come with me.

05:03.500 --> 05:04.420
I'll leave matters

05:05.350 --> 05:07.230
in the Mortal World to you.

05:08.790 --> 05:09.990
No problem, Great Ancestor.

05:51.350 --> 05:52.190
Do not come near me.

05:52.670 --> 05:53.510
You are too filthy.

06:22.030 --> 06:23.910
You're nothing

06:24.110 --> 06:25.550
but a sickly fraud living off others.

06:26.060 --> 06:27.670
How do you have such power?

06:29.150 --> 06:29.990
Your Grace,

06:30.230 --> 06:31.070
to be honest,

06:31.910 --> 06:32.963
back then, Master Qingxuan,

06:32.974 --> 06:34.068
out of pity for Great Liang

06:34.079 --> 06:35.242
with only half its land left,

06:35.420 --> 06:36.990
wished to keep the imperial clan safe.

06:37.350 --> 06:38.860
After repeated requests,

06:39.060 --> 06:40.260
I reluctantly agreed

06:40.260 --> 06:41.820
to leave Starhaven Sect and come here

06:41.990 --> 06:43.260
to serve as your Prophet.

06:44.230 --> 06:45.300
Times have changed.

06:45.620 --> 06:46.500
People these days

06:46.500 --> 06:47.550
have actually forgotten

06:47.820 --> 06:48.740
that my family name

06:49.670 --> 06:50.740
is Hejia.

06:52.670 --> 06:53.590
Your son died

06:53.590 --> 06:54.590
a month ago.

06:55.590 --> 06:57.206
For power and glory,

06:57.217 --> 06:58.676
you forged a pact with an evil spirit

06:59.230 --> 07:01.110
to keep up the lie that he lives.

07:06.030 --> 07:07.030
The obsessions on you

07:07.030 --> 07:08.470
are far too heavy.

07:11.820 --> 07:13.590
Why not let me take them?

07:30.180 --> 07:31.180
Song Xingyu,

07:31.550 --> 07:33.110
you truly are something.

07:34.260 --> 07:35.710
You dared to control a prince.

07:36.990 --> 07:38.940
Do you mean to rule the Mortal World?

07:40.030 --> 07:41.710
What joy is the Void alone?

07:42.420 --> 07:44.150
The Mortal World is far more fun.

07:44.820 --> 07:46.180
The ruler of the Mortal World

07:46.990 --> 07:48.150
controls everything

07:48.420 --> 07:49.740
that mortals have.

07:51.420 --> 07:52.550
Not a bad idea.

07:53.550 --> 07:55.150
Who told you to do that?

07:56.660 --> 07:59.380
(Forbidden)

08:08.110 --> 08:09.990
You made a pact with that person.

08:10.380 --> 08:11.220
The pact binds you,

08:11.230 --> 08:12.740
so you can't speak his name.

08:13.590 --> 08:14.590
I understand.

08:20.710 --> 08:21.620
I...

08:21.620 --> 08:22.820
I know the former Sovereign

08:22.820 --> 08:23.740
didn't die for love.

08:24.710 --> 08:25.710
In the Sovereign's Hall,

08:26.339 --> 08:27.352
there was another spirit.

08:28.670 --> 08:29.550
Tell me.

08:30.990 --> 08:31.830
Who was it?

08:55.780 --> 08:57.710
Do you think I don't know

08:58.990 --> 09:00.620
something's off with my father's death?

09:05.780 --> 09:07.230
My father loved my mother

09:08.740 --> 09:09.580
and me.

09:11.350 --> 09:13.070
He promised to stay by my side,

09:14.780 --> 09:16.110
so he'd never have left me

09:16.110 --> 09:17.350
with a chaotic, unfamiliar Void

09:17.350 --> 09:18.900
and die for love.

09:25.230 --> 09:26.070
Great Ancestor,

09:27.190 --> 09:28.350
he just said

09:30.740 --> 09:31.660
the former Sovereign...

09:37.140 --> 09:38.350
I'll take Consort Yu back.

09:45.430 --> 09:46.270
Let's go.

10:01.310 --> 10:02.150
Ziji,

10:04.350 --> 10:05.396
how old are you this year?

10:08.260 --> 10:09.100
Twenty.

10:09.430 --> 10:10.470
What's your zodiac sign?

10:18.070 --> 10:19.230
You can't even remember

10:19.230 --> 10:20.140
your own zodiac sign?

10:20.990 --> 10:22.380
Are you truly only twenty?

10:26.900 --> 10:27.780
You're like me.

10:28.830 --> 10:29.670
You're not a mortal.

10:31.590 --> 10:33.310
In fact, I don't care who you are.

10:34.830 --> 10:35.990
Fengyi has grown up.

10:36.590 --> 10:38.070
He doesn't need me to decide for him.

10:39.230 --> 10:40.070
Whatever you are,

10:41.140 --> 10:42.362
he must've kept you by his side

10:42.373 --> 10:43.430
for a reason.

10:45.110 --> 10:46.020
Fengyi has never been

10:46.710 --> 10:48.310
an easy child to raise.

10:49.310 --> 10:50.230
He's deeply curious,

10:50.900 --> 10:51.830
but frail in body,

10:52.500 --> 10:53.500
plagued by illness.

10:53.500 --> 10:54.470
He may not live long.

10:55.990 --> 10:57.590
The road ahead is his to walk.

11:00.020 --> 11:01.380
I only hope that by his side,

11:02.660 --> 11:03.780
you can look after him.

11:24.740 --> 11:27.190
In the Shunzhou horse graft,

11:27.845 --> 11:29.625
Sun Changde,
Registrar of the Imperial Stud,

11:29.636 --> 11:30.706
has changed his testimony.

11:31.380 --> 11:32.500
He says he was ordered

11:32.500 --> 11:34.430
to frame Sun Zi'an, Minister of War,

11:34.590 --> 11:36.230
and Li Li,
Minister of the Imperial Stud.

11:36.590 --> 11:37.710
The one who ordered him

11:38.230 --> 11:41.140
is Duan Xu, Court Counselor.

11:42.230 --> 11:43.070
Duan Xu,

11:43.453 --> 11:44.600
do you have anything to say?

11:46.350 --> 11:47.190
Your Majesty,

11:48.190 --> 11:49.030
I did no such thing.

11:52.900 --> 11:53.830
Your Majesty,

11:54.620 --> 11:57.020
the horse craft has indeed festered

11:57.660 --> 11:59.020
for ten years.

11:59.860 --> 12:01.350
By Your Majesty's command,

12:01.653 --> 12:02.852
I have investigated this case.

12:02.990 --> 12:03.830
The chief culprits

12:03.830 --> 12:05.710
are Sun Zi'an, Minister of War,

12:06.003 --> 12:07.669
and Li Li,
Minister of the Imperial Stud,

12:08.070 --> 12:09.660
not the Court Counselor.

12:09.900 --> 12:10.830
So, it is true.

12:11.310 --> 12:12.710
The proof must be solid.

12:13.110 --> 12:14.276
According to Sun Changde,

12:14.287 --> 12:15.533
Registrar of the Imperial Stud,

12:15.710 --> 12:16.860
several months ago,

12:17.070 --> 12:18.830
he found 3,000 warhorses
drawing false pay

12:19.020 --> 12:21.230
in Shunzhou's horse ledgers.

12:21.710 --> 12:23.620
So, he prosecuted
Sun Zi'an with evidence.

12:23.950 --> 12:25.310
But after the inquisition,

12:25.660 --> 12:27.660
Sun Changde was coerced by Sun Zi'an,

12:27.660 --> 12:28.590
changed his testimony,

12:28.900 --> 12:30.129
and falsely claimed it was done

12:30.140 --> 12:31.273
by Duan Xu, Court Counselor.

12:31.860 --> 12:32.700
This case

12:32.950 --> 12:34.230
involves the Ministry of War

12:34.780 --> 12:36.660
and a prince.

12:36.786 --> 12:37.950
The Ministry of War was in it.

12:37.950 --> 12:38.790
This...

12:41.669 --> 12:42.635
By Your Majesty's order,

12:42.646 --> 12:44.893
I searched the Sun Mansion
and the 5th Prince's Mansion.

12:44.904 --> 12:46.304
I found all the solid evidence

12:46.315 --> 12:47.225
in the horse graft.

12:47.740 --> 12:49.860
Now, the 5th Prince,
ashamed before the realm,

12:50.620 --> 12:52.140
has taken his own life in apology.

12:56.020 --> 12:56.860
Good!

12:57.500 --> 12:59.140
Your Majesty, please calm your anger.

13:02.830 --> 13:03.670
And you,

13:04.500 --> 13:05.350
Qin Huanda.

13:08.140 --> 13:08.980
Yes, Your Majesty.

13:09.230 --> 13:10.780
As Marshal of the Three Armies,

13:11.310 --> 13:12.710
were you truly unaware?

13:13.020 --> 13:13.900
I beg your wisdom.

13:14.660 --> 13:15.900
I've long been tied to wars,

13:16.083 --> 13:17.016
with no time for papers.

13:17.350 --> 13:18.903
Horse administration has long suffered,

13:19.110 --> 13:20.710
but war was graver.

13:21.110 --> 13:22.140
Forgive my oversight.

13:24.310 --> 13:25.150
Your Majesty,

13:26.860 --> 13:28.380
Marshal Qin makes it sound easy.

13:28.860 --> 13:30.110
I can't agree.

13:30.470 --> 13:31.780
Before Yunzhou was retaken,

13:32.260 --> 13:33.350
we had no natural pasture.

13:33.660 --> 13:34.613
Any horse ranch we built

13:34.660 --> 13:36.020
took land from the people's fields.

13:36.350 --> 13:37.380
The land for one horse

13:37.620 --> 13:38.470
could feed 25 people.

13:38.780 --> 13:39.660
3,000 horses

13:39.990 --> 13:41.350
means 75,000 people.

13:41.740 --> 13:42.920
Corrupt officials have killed

13:43.350 --> 13:44.780
those 75,000 people

13:44.950 --> 13:46.110
due to their greed.

13:46.380 --> 13:48.540
I was at the front, short on warhorses.

13:48.780 --> 13:50.026
The cavalry couldn't form ranks.

13:50.043 --> 13:51.245
We'd only send surprise troops

13:51.256 --> 13:52.616
instead of facing the foe head-on.

13:52.900 --> 13:54.286
Every victory came at a grave cost.

13:54.500 --> 13:55.620
Our troop losses doubled.

13:57.710 --> 13:59.110
Did Marshal Qin not see any of this?

13:59.540 --> 14:00.693
How can we defend the realm?

14:00.900 --> 14:02.340
- You...
- Your Majesty,

14:03.140 --> 14:05.260
as the Marshal of the Three Armies,

14:05.590 --> 14:06.500
Marshal Qin is good

14:06.830 --> 14:07.830
at driving the foe away.

14:08.260 --> 14:09.740
He reclaimed our lost land.

14:10.070 --> 14:11.230
If, over one brief oversight,

14:11.230 --> 14:12.500
we place false charges on him,

14:13.070 --> 14:15.660
I fear the army's hearts will grow cold.

14:16.500 --> 14:17.470
If not for Duan Xu,

14:17.860 --> 14:20.190
who struck Yuzhou and Liangzhou

14:20.716 --> 14:22.083
with a few thousand against many,

14:22.260 --> 14:23.260
crossed the Guanhe River,

14:23.660 --> 14:25.070
and pushed on into Shuozhou,

14:25.263 --> 14:26.683
taking command in the darkest hour,

14:26.694 --> 14:28.138
and reclaiming Yunzhou and Luozhou,

14:28.149 --> 14:29.383
would Qin Huanda have won

14:29.710 --> 14:31.260
such towering merit today?

14:31.740 --> 14:32.710
Your Majesty,

14:32.923 --> 14:35.522
horse administration is tied closely
to military administration.

14:35.620 --> 14:37.620
Marshal Qin failed to spot its flaws.

14:37.620 --> 14:38.700
That was a neglect of duty.

14:38.950 --> 14:40.430
Though his merits are great,

14:40.590 --> 14:41.860
he should still be punished.

14:42.950 --> 14:43.790
Duke Pei,

14:44.230 --> 14:46.020
what do you think?

14:46.350 --> 14:47.190
I've spent

14:47.370 --> 14:49.830
half my life in military administration,

14:50.350 --> 14:52.710
yet I failed
to remind Marshal Qin of it.

14:52.870 --> 14:53.710
I failed

14:53.710 --> 14:55.110
in my duty to detect it.

14:55.380 --> 14:56.830
Please punish me.

14:59.430 --> 15:00.900
In the horse graft,

15:01.740 --> 15:03.110
Han Mingxuan is now dead.

15:03.590 --> 15:04.500
His co-conspirators,

15:04.500 --> 15:06.070
Sun Zi'an, Minister of War,

15:06.716 --> 15:08.398
and Li Li,
Minister of the Imperial Stud,

15:08.470 --> 15:09.620
misused their power

15:09.950 --> 15:11.116
and took vast illicit wealth.

15:11.310 --> 15:12.380
That is unforgivable.

15:12.830 --> 15:15.380
They shall be beheaded.

15:16.470 --> 15:17.710
The other officials involved

15:17.710 --> 15:19.310
will be tried by the Judicial Review

15:19.900 --> 15:21.190
and dealt with by the law.

15:24.950 --> 15:25.790
I'll keep

15:25.990 --> 15:27.380
the military tally for now.

15:28.110 --> 15:30.190
When war comes in the future,

15:31.380 --> 15:32.660
I'll make arrangements.

15:33.710 --> 15:34.550
Duan Xu.

15:36.900 --> 15:37.740
Yes, Your Majesty.

15:37.990 --> 15:38.830
From this day on,

15:39.140 --> 15:40.620
the horse administration

15:41.350 --> 15:42.990
will be in your charge.

15:43.430 --> 15:44.350
Yes, Your Majesty.

15:48.500 --> 15:49.350
Just now, you were

15:49.350 --> 15:50.710
in high spirits at the court.

15:51.380 --> 15:53.190
The case was handled well.

15:53.780 --> 15:54.830
Thanks to my two

15:54.830 --> 15:55.710
steadfast supporters.

15:56.710 --> 15:58.620
Even the 5th Prince was involved.

15:58.620 --> 15:59.460
Indeed.

15:59.740 --> 16:01.190
It is truly shocking.

16:07.350 --> 16:08.190
Mr. Wang,

16:09.190 --> 16:10.030
may Great Liang know

16:10.466 --> 16:11.666
no injustice under your lead.

16:14.350 --> 16:15.190
What puzzles me is

16:15.950 --> 16:16.830
how you learned

16:16.990 --> 16:18.419
the remaining evidence was hidden

16:18.430 --> 16:19.710
in the 5th Prince's Mansion.

16:22.020 --> 16:22.860
An immortal told me.

16:25.350 --> 16:26.500
You're about to marry.

16:27.070 --> 16:27.910
I offer

16:28.140 --> 16:29.470
my congratulations first.

16:42.140 --> 16:42.990
How about this one?

16:48.900 --> 16:49.740
What about this?

16:53.710 --> 16:55.260
These are all too ordinary.

16:59.710 --> 17:00.550
This one.

17:01.710 --> 17:04.230
This is Radiant Cyan Brocade.

17:04.470 --> 17:05.630
It gleams with shifting colors

17:05.630 --> 17:07.540
and fits the body on its own.

17:07.740 --> 17:09.870
Perfect for Mr. Duan's wedding robes.

17:13.260 --> 17:14.100
Ugly.

17:17.100 --> 17:17.940
This one?

17:18.390 --> 17:20.020
I spent a hundred years

17:20.020 --> 17:22.390
finding this Wandering Ice Pillow.

17:22.820 --> 17:24.870
Its color is bright and lustrous.

17:25.150 --> 17:27.500
Rest on it, and all the isles and lakes

17:27.500 --> 17:28.500
will fill your dreams.

17:28.670 --> 17:29.990
It's just right for Mr. Duan

17:29.990 --> 17:32.740
sleeping beside his dear wife.

17:33.060 --> 17:33.900
Well?

17:41.740 --> 17:42.580
How dull.

17:58.430 --> 18:02.470
The air is dry. Beware of fire.

18:33.470 --> 18:34.630
Someone has died again.

18:46.740 --> 18:48.700
(Erudite and Determined)

18:57.020 --> 18:57.860
Your instinct

18:57.860 --> 18:59.100
is still as sharp as ever.

19:23.820 --> 19:24.660
Is it you?

19:28.430 --> 19:29.270
You said

19:30.710 --> 19:31.740
that if disaster struck

19:33.630 --> 19:35.230
or I needed help,

19:36.630 --> 19:37.950
once I called your name,

19:38.580 --> 19:39.420
you would appear.

19:40.450 --> 19:41.300
Did you hear

19:41.300 --> 19:42.300
my heart calling for you

19:44.230 --> 19:45.070
and come?

19:49.020 --> 19:50.340
What would you like?

19:52.670 --> 19:53.510
Your Grace,

19:55.500 --> 19:56.340
I like you.

20:04.190 --> 20:05.100
That won't do.

20:05.990 --> 20:07.710
There is something on my mind.

20:09.150 --> 20:10.820
You never ask why I love you.

20:12.630 --> 20:13.470
Perhaps it's because

20:13.670 --> 20:15.340
too many adore you,

20:15.910 --> 20:16.950
and you are used to it.

20:17.740 --> 20:19.230
So, you're not curious

20:19.950 --> 20:20.790
about my reasons.

20:30.430 --> 20:31.270
You drew me in.

20:34.260 --> 20:35.990
With the tenderness beneath your cold,

20:37.340 --> 20:38.780
the loneliness above all spirits,

20:39.870 --> 20:41.150
and your love for this world,

20:42.100 --> 20:42.990
you drew me in.

20:46.260 --> 20:47.390
And I took the bait

20:48.740 --> 20:49.710
willingly.

20:50.990 --> 20:51.950
Will you miss me?

20:53.190 --> 20:54.910
Since I left the Void until now,

20:55.580 --> 20:56.780
I have missed you often.

20:57.486 --> 20:58.789
Every day, in every little thing,

20:58.800 --> 20:59.670
you come to my mind.

21:01.020 --> 21:02.500
That day, I met you on the street.

21:05.670 --> 21:06.910
You asked me who I was.

21:07.870 --> 21:08.710
Though I knew

21:08.710 --> 21:09.820
you were playing dumb,

21:10.100 --> 21:11.230
I still thought

21:12.580 --> 21:13.630
that perhaps one day,

21:15.230 --> 21:16.260
you might forget

21:17.780 --> 21:19.150
my name,

21:20.300 --> 21:21.580
my appearance,

21:23.540 --> 21:24.380
and me.

21:31.100 --> 21:32.150
By the time that day comes,

21:36.190 --> 21:37.540
I will have long turned to dust.

21:38.780 --> 21:40.206
I will no longer be able to hold you

21:41.340 --> 21:42.580
and tell you who I am.

21:50.710 --> 21:52.150
I think that would be unfair.

21:55.230 --> 21:56.500
You must rarely think of me.

21:57.500 --> 21:58.870
That is why you forget so easily.

22:00.260 --> 22:02.150
If only you missed me as I miss you,

22:02.150 --> 22:05.310
♪Spring comes; ice and snow thaw♪

22:08.876 --> 22:10.536
you'd remember me
for at least 100 years.

22:16.310 --> 22:20.780
♪In the season at its fullest♪

22:21.810 --> 22:28.080
♪Light the lamps
to pierce the old night♪

22:32.650 --> 22:39.560
♪Borrow mortal warmth to ease the cold♪

22:40.040 --> 22:46.980
♪Warm winds bring fragrant blooms,
savoring wine and graceful dances♪

22:47.300 --> 22:51.210
♪Let me love with all my heart♪

22:52.260 --> 22:53.100
Simu,

22:55.540 --> 22:56.380
are you still here?

22:58.220 --> 23:02.610
♪Still shining bright♪

23:02.890 --> 23:05.560
♪With you by my side♪

23:17.540 --> 23:18.380
Have you left?

23:19.980 --> 23:23.590
♪Falling into your gentle smile♪

23:25.630 --> 23:26.820
You don't even talk to me.

23:27.270 --> 23:31.320
♪In your eyes♪

23:34.560 --> 23:37.240
♪If you'd let me know how tell♪

23:37.340 --> 23:38.260
Foxy,

23:41.780 --> 23:43.060
I am quite busy.

23:43.540 --> 23:46.600
♪Love and worry♪

23:46.740 --> 23:48.630
But I do miss you sometimes.

23:49.130 --> 23:56.160
♪Borrow mortal warmth to ease the cold♪

23:56.380 --> 23:58.780
♪Warm winds bring fragrant blooms♪

23:59.060 --> 24:00.240
I often think of you.

24:00.240 --> 24:03.480
♪Savoring wine and graceful dances♪

24:03.600 --> 24:10.600
♪Let me love with all my heart
in youthful grace♪

24:10.880 --> 24:13.470
♪With light, carefree words♪

24:13.540 --> 24:14.740
I still do not know

24:16.630 --> 24:18.820
what wedding gift to give you.

24:20.420 --> 24:25.590
♪A pot of wine in fleeting dreams♪

24:27.170 --> 24:35.720
♪A brief life dares seek eternity♪

24:37.300 --> 24:40.740
(Half a month later)

24:43.640 --> 24:50.620
♪May I roam drunk in dreams
and never forget♪

24:50.840 --> 24:54.740
♪Please ferry me once♪

24:55.100 --> 24:58.140
(Duan Mansion)

24:58.140 --> 25:00.900
(Joy)

25:01.760 --> 25:08.160
♪I see a ray♪

25:11.740 --> 25:12.580
He's out.

25:13.780 --> 25:16.460
(Duan Mansion)

25:20.060 --> 25:24.020
(Duan Mansion)

25:39.190 --> 25:40.990
The Duan clan gave me

25:40.990 --> 25:42.430
a wedding invitation.

25:43.300 --> 25:44.740
It's more official

25:44.740 --> 25:45.630
than your hair ribbon.

25:47.020 --> 25:48.260
And now, I can only stand here

25:48.260 --> 25:49.100
with you,

25:49.470 --> 25:50.950
watching the bridegroom from afar.

25:51.190 --> 25:52.580
I can't even join the fun below.

25:54.670 --> 25:56.020
Go attend the wedding feast.

25:56.580 --> 25:57.740
I didn't ask you to be here.

26:01.020 --> 26:02.150
Since this is

26:02.740 --> 26:03.870
your first time

26:03.870 --> 26:04.710
at a wedding,

26:04.870 --> 26:05.816
I'll keep you company.

26:11.780 --> 26:12.620
They're coming.

26:13.150 --> 26:13.990
They're coming.

26:54.990 --> 26:56.083
They're fetching the bride.

26:56.826 --> 26:57.780
The folks in the streets

26:57.780 --> 26:58.950
gain nothing from it.

26:59.710 --> 27:00.756
What makes them so happy?

27:01.780 --> 27:03.390
They are sharing in the wedding joy.

27:04.100 --> 27:06.230
To share in happy news,
or let others share it,

27:06.580 --> 27:08.230
is a blessing.

27:15.390 --> 27:17.190
(What does a wedding truly mean?)

27:19.150 --> 27:20.500
(Why did you insist on making me)

27:20.500 --> 27:21.580
(attend your wedding?)

27:31.780 --> 27:33.470
Congratulations, Mr. Duan.

27:33.910 --> 27:35.470
Congratulations, Mr. Duan.

27:36.190 --> 27:37.870
Congratulations, Mr. Duan.

27:57.900 --> 28:03.760
♪Touched memories linger like shadows♪

28:04.390 --> 28:09.900
♪Scattered reflections
sink into my heart♪

28:10.490 --> 28:16.500
♪If I could softly call you like this♪

28:17.590 --> 28:22.200
♪As gentle as a fleeting embrace♪

28:23.700 --> 28:29.350
♪Though apart, my thoughts still swirl♪

28:29.970 --> 28:35.590
♪A lifetime is given
for a name to be remembered♪

28:36.120 --> 28:39.480
♪There are passions and pains♪

28:39.680 --> 28:42.580
♪Hope we'll experience them together♪

28:43.260 --> 28:48.970
♪Before we forget or grow apart♪

28:48.990 --> 28:49.870
Foxy,

28:51.150 --> 28:52.230
you look stunning

28:53.820 --> 28:54.780
in red.

28:55.210 --> 28:58.040
♪What would come of it?♪

28:58.450 --> 28:59.950
♪I care for no one but you♪

28:59.950 --> 29:01.600
♪I'll come near and run to you♪

29:01.600 --> 29:04.780
♪To heal the deepest wounds♪

29:06.670 --> 29:07.510
(Simu,)

29:09.230 --> 29:10.070
(did you see it?)

29:12.540 --> 29:13.815
(I want the first thing you see)

29:13.826 --> 29:15.430
(to be me in wedding attire)

29:17.470 --> 29:18.780
(in this vibrant world.)

29:37.230 --> 29:42.640
♪Though apart, my thoughts still swirl♪

29:43.530 --> 29:49.170
♪A lifetime is given
for a name to be remembered♪

29:49.670 --> 29:52.980
♪There are passions and pains♪

29:53.780 --> 29:54.740
You helped him.

29:56.056 --> 29:57.390
Blessed flowers can stir the Pearl

29:57.390 --> 29:58.416
to trade the five senses.

29:59.260 --> 30:00.190
Just now, he gave me

30:01.820 --> 30:03.020
the sense of color.

30:03.890 --> 30:05.430
♪Grows dim and fades away♪

30:05.740 --> 30:06.740
Heaven as my witness,

30:08.230 --> 30:10.580
you made that pact yourselves.

30:10.820 --> 30:12.540
You set the terms yourselves.

30:13.020 --> 30:13.870
As for me,

30:15.430 --> 30:16.780
I merely did

30:17.190 --> 30:18.470
a little catalyzing.

30:20.060 --> 30:20.900
So,

30:21.500 --> 30:22.870
this was your plan.

30:24.950 --> 30:26.340
But now, with color,

30:27.500 --> 30:28.580
you're far too beautiful.

30:30.580 --> 30:31.420
Great Ancestor,

30:32.060 --> 30:32.900
what did you say?

30:46.540 --> 30:47.780
He gave me his sense of color.

30:48.340 --> 30:49.300
Now, all he can see

30:49.300 --> 30:50.140
is black and white.

30:50.340 --> 30:51.990
Then how will he see his bride?

30:57.670 --> 30:59.780
True.

31:06.780 --> 31:07.780
- Good.
- Mr. Wang.

31:07.780 --> 31:08.910
Come this way, please.

31:10.430 --> 31:11.950
From now on, we're family.

31:12.220 --> 31:13.060
Please, please.

31:13.060 --> 31:14.910
We're family. How nice.

31:26.060 --> 31:27.060
Assassin!

31:27.430 --> 31:28.430
Guards, hurry!

31:30.280 --> 31:31.150
What happened?

31:31.150 --> 31:32.340
What's going on?

31:32.820 --> 31:34.020
Let go of Miss Wang!

31:34.020 --> 31:35.020
- Milady!
- Stand back.

31:35.020 --> 31:35.860
Let go!

31:35.860 --> 31:37.020
(Wang Mansion)

31:37.020 --> 31:37.910
All of you, step back!

31:38.580 --> 31:39.420
What do we do now?

31:40.390 --> 31:41.670
If anyone moves, she dies!

31:44.020 --> 31:44.860
Don't move!

31:46.470 --> 31:47.310
Move aside!

31:49.670 --> 31:50.540
Don't move!

31:52.190 --> 31:53.030
Go!

31:57.630 --> 31:59.260
Milady! Milady!

31:59.390 --> 32:00.390
What are we to do?

32:00.390 --> 32:02.390
- She was taken!
- Report it!

32:03.100 --> 32:04.340
The Chong people are in Nandu!

32:04.740 --> 32:05.710
They seized the bride!

32:06.100 --> 32:08.060
Shut the gates. Seize them!

32:08.060 --> 32:09.060
- Yes.
- Go!

32:15.820 --> 32:17.260
Follow that bride and the assassin.

32:18.300 --> 32:19.580
Isn't that a bad idea?

32:20.430 --> 32:21.710
Do as I say.

32:23.950 --> 32:25.150
This doesn't concern spirits.

32:25.580 --> 32:27.780
Let's not meddle in this, then.

32:28.670 --> 32:30.230
If I still had spirit power,

32:30.580 --> 32:31.780
would it be your turn?

32:33.740 --> 32:34.870
Did you forget

32:34.870 --> 32:36.300
how I lost my spirit power?

32:38.020 --> 32:38.860
All right.

32:58.190 --> 32:59.030
Where did they go?

33:02.470 --> 33:03.310
He Xiaoxiao.

33:05.950 --> 33:06.790
Miss He.

33:08.500 --> 33:10.950
I am Prophet Hejia.

33:11.470 --> 33:13.470
Are you well, Miss Wang?

33:30.260 --> 33:31.780
Prophet Hejia, please spare me.

33:32.670 --> 33:33.510
Get up.

33:34.950 --> 33:35.790
Suyi.

33:39.390 --> 33:40.990
Suyi, get up.

33:46.580 --> 33:47.420
Given the situation,

33:47.990 --> 33:49.430
I alone will bear all the blame.

33:49.910 --> 33:51.060
Seize me if you must.

33:51.740 --> 33:53.580
You are a fragrance maker
at Yueran Fragrance.

33:54.540 --> 33:55.670
So, this man

33:55.950 --> 33:56.990
is your beloved?

33:57.500 --> 33:59.820
Xuan and I are devoted to each other.

34:00.340 --> 34:01.820
But bound by our different stations,

34:02.020 --> 34:03.190
we dared not make it public.

34:05.500 --> 34:06.870
Prophet Hejia, please help us

34:07.100 --> 34:08.100
and let us leave.

34:09.430 --> 34:10.270
Great Ancestor,

34:11.020 --> 34:12.060
this.

34:12.900 --> 34:13.750
Duan Xu knew

34:13.750 --> 34:15.220
you wanted to marry him,

34:15.990 --> 34:17.060
so he cast aside his pride

34:17.350 --> 34:18.870
and staged this whole farce

34:19.750 --> 34:20.910
to make it happen for you.

34:23.390 --> 34:25.180
Mr. Duan arranged it with me

34:25.500 --> 34:26.990
to help Xuan and me carry this out.

34:27.660 --> 34:28.500
He said

34:28.910 --> 34:30.140
he'd seen too much

34:30.350 --> 34:31.580
of so-called mutual respect

34:31.580 --> 34:32.500
and fake affection.

34:32.830 --> 34:34.060
He found it unbearably dull.

34:35.430 --> 34:36.910
He, too, had someone in his heart.

34:37.950 --> 34:38.870
He also said

34:39.350 --> 34:40.750
she was the girl he loved most.

34:41.660 --> 34:42.500
Perhaps

34:42.910 --> 34:44.350
that girl would never marry him.

34:44.790 --> 34:45.750
Then he would

34:46.270 --> 34:47.910
remain unmarried all his life.

34:52.180 --> 34:53.390
Miss Wang and Xuan

34:53.390 --> 34:54.230
are in love.

34:55.060 --> 34:55.950
Xu had us put on

34:55.950 --> 34:57.100
such a grand performance.

34:57.430 --> 34:58.660
He helped Miss Wang,

34:59.020 --> 34:59.910
as well as himself

34:59.910 --> 35:01.020
and the one he loves.

35:01.700 --> 35:02.580
You should understand

35:02.580 --> 35:03.500
his intention.

35:23.580 --> 35:24.420
Go.

35:25.430 --> 35:26.270
Go.

35:27.180 --> 35:28.020
Where is he?

35:39.460 --> 35:42.580
(Duan Mansion)

35:42.580 --> 35:45.140
(Letter of Challenge)

35:45.140 --> 35:46.060
The bride

35:46.060 --> 35:48.060
was seized by Chong spies.

35:49.660 --> 35:51.580
I heard it was because Duan Xu

35:51.910 --> 35:54.660
drew too much notice
on the northern battlefield,

35:55.060 --> 35:56.870
so the Chong spies took the bride

35:56.870 --> 35:57.950
to get even

35:58.180 --> 35:59.540
and shame him.

35:59.990 --> 36:01.060
They've gone too far.

36:01.620 --> 36:03.350
Mr. Wang nearly fainted from rage.

36:04.790 --> 36:06.540
His daughter is the true victim.

36:07.310 --> 36:08.700
That's right.

36:09.830 --> 36:10.670
Xu,

36:10.950 --> 36:11.790
how is it?

36:12.100 --> 36:13.270
Have you found the bride?

36:18.020 --> 36:19.310
- What to do?
- What do we do?

36:21.060 --> 36:22.100
Those North Chong spies.

36:24.660 --> 36:26.060
Those wretched North Chong spies.

36:26.060 --> 36:27.140
They are truly vile.

36:36.990 --> 36:38.870
- Gentlemen.
- Since you're here,

36:40.750 --> 36:41.830
please bear witness for me.

36:46.950 --> 36:48.310
The Chong people stole our land,

36:49.660 --> 36:50.700
enslaved our people,

36:51.540 --> 36:52.620
and harmed my kin.

36:53.220 --> 36:54.500
Now, they've seized my bride

36:54.950 --> 36:56.580
and sent a letter of challenge.

36:57.390 --> 36:58.270
I will never

36:58.700 --> 36:59.620
forgive them for this.

37:01.620 --> 37:03.220
Wang, bride of the Duan clan,

37:03.500 --> 37:04.500
is virtuous and gentle.

37:05.100 --> 37:06.580
Today, she suffers this calamity

37:08.020 --> 37:09.950
all because of me.

37:12.060 --> 37:13.310
I can't face her

37:14.310 --> 37:15.950
or my honored in-laws.

37:17.910 --> 37:19.060
If she returns safely,

37:20.310 --> 37:22.180
I will never take a concubine.

37:25.270 --> 37:26.310
If she can't return,

37:28.100 --> 37:29.620
and we can't fulfill our bond,

37:30.270 --> 37:31.620
I swear

37:32.580 --> 37:34.990
by Duan ancestors' honor:

37:36.430 --> 37:37.700
For as long as I fail to drive

37:37.700 --> 37:39.180
the Chong people from Great Liang,

37:39.750 --> 37:41.180
I won't take another wife.

37:42.060 --> 37:42.900
How could he?

37:43.180 --> 37:44.660
How can he do this?

37:48.060 --> 37:49.180
If I break this oath,

37:50.790 --> 37:51.830
I shall meet a tragic end.

37:52.700 --> 37:53.910
He can't live without an heir.

37:54.470 --> 37:55.310
Exactly!

37:57.580 --> 37:58.700
Why go this far?

37:59.140 --> 38:00.790
Utterly unfilial.

38:01.470 --> 38:02.700
North Chong

38:02.990 --> 38:04.140
has gone too far!

38:10.220 --> 38:14.580
(Duan Mansion)

38:14.580 --> 38:15.430
I never expected

38:15.990 --> 38:16.950
Mr. Duan to be

38:16.950 --> 38:18.540
so devoted to Miss Wang.

38:19.220 --> 38:20.470
Such a harsh oath.

38:20.830 --> 38:21.790
Mr. Duan

38:21.790 --> 38:22.950
was so distraught.

38:23.100 --> 38:24.350
I fear he truly meant it.

38:24.900 --> 38:25.750
But Duan Xu

38:25.750 --> 38:27.060
is the Duan clan's only heir.

38:27.750 --> 38:29.060
If he truly never marries,

38:29.310 --> 38:30.990
won't the Duan line end?

38:31.270 --> 38:32.750
Exactly.

38:55.340 --> 38:58.270
♪I go alone in the night without end♪

38:58.580 --> 39:02.020
♪I can't remember the seasons
or the passing years♪

39:03.100 --> 39:06.310
♪Wishful thoughts creep onto my brows♪

39:06.770 --> 39:10.200
♪Whose face is it♪

39:10.640 --> 39:13.790
♪Through cycles of time, we get to meet♪

39:14.570 --> 39:17.570
♪Snow on sunny days♪

39:17.970 --> 39:20.400
♪Countless wayfarers roam the world♪

39:20.400 --> 39:27.340
♪Luckily, I share a fate with you♪

39:29.550 --> 39:33.490
♪I hold a lantern to draw the moon♪

39:33.490 --> 39:37.490
♪Light up the night that haunts you♪

39:37.810 --> 39:41.830
♪I have simple wishes, but I fear♪

39:42.220 --> 39:43.060
Simu.

39:44.980 --> 39:48.560
♪You always stay with me♪

39:48.940 --> 39:52.790
♪See the world I've never seen♪

39:53.390 --> 39:57.360
♪However the years may wind♪

39:57.360 --> 40:05.360
♪I wish I could live in your heart♪

40:22.240 --> 40:27.570
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

40:27.900 --> 40:32.150
♪Light encountered shadow♪

40:33.510 --> 40:38.880
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

40:39.180 --> 40:43.780
♪The unbreakable fate♪

40:44.870 --> 40:46.710
♪Suddenly cracked♪

40:58.920 --> 41:04.360
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

41:04.540 --> 41:08.870
♪Light encountered shadow♪

41:10.240 --> 41:15.630
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

41:15.860 --> 41:19.800
♪The unbreakable fate♪

41:21.570 --> 41:23.460
♪Suddenly cracked♪

41:26.120 --> 41:29.280
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

41:29.280 --> 41:31.810
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

41:31.810 --> 41:37.330
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

41:37.330 --> 41:40.570
♪Following fate's guidance♪

41:40.570 --> 41:45.430
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

41:45.770 --> 41:48.790
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

41:48.790 --> 41:51.610
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

41:51.870 --> 41:54.400
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

41:54.400 --> 41:59.820
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

41:59.990 --> 42:03.060
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

42:03.220 --> 42:08.120
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

42:08.330 --> 42:11.800
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
